{
  "video_id": "xHHb7R3kx40",
  "title": "Why fascism is so tempting -- and how your data could power it | Yuval Noah Harari",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12968.0,
      "end_time": 14118.0,
      "text": "Hello, everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15562.0,
      "end_time": 20497.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a bit funny, because I did write that humans will become digital,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20522.0,
      "end_time": 23235.0,
      "text": "but I didn&#39;t think it will happen so fast"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 24919.0,
      "text": "and that it will happen to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25649.0,
      "end_time": 28331.0,
      "text": "But here I am, as a digital avatar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28355.0,
      "end_time": 31210.0,
      "text": "and here you are, so let&#39;s start."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32700.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34203.0,
      "text": "And let&#39;s start with a question."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34823.0,
      "end_time": 38357.0,
      "text": "How many fascists are there in the audience today?"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38381.0,
      "end_time": 39831.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39855.0,
      "end_time": 42203.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s a bit difficult to say,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42228.0,
      "end_time": 45695.0,
      "text": "because we&#39;ve forgotten what fascism is."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 46498.0,
      "end_time": 49770.0,
      "text": "People now use the term \"fascist\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 49101.0,
      "end_time": 52109.0,
      "text": "as a kind of general-purpose abuse."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 52133.0,
      "end_time": 56800.0,
      "text": "Or they confuse fascism with nationalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56863.0,
      "end_time": 62251.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s take a few minutes to clarify what fascism actually is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62275.0,
      "end_time": 65394.0,
      "text": "and how it is different from nationalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65838.0,
      "end_time": 70878.0,
      "text": "The milder forms of nationalism have been among the most benevolent"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 70903.0,
      "end_time": 72361.0,
      "text": "of human creations."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 72990.0,
      "end_time": 77101.0,
      "text": "Nations are communities of millions of strangers"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 77125.0,
      "end_time": 78838.0,
      "text": "who don&#39;t really know each other."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79489.0,
      "end_time": 82894.0,
      "text": "For example, I don&#39;t know the eight million people"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 82918.0,
      "end_time": 85474.0,
      "text": "who share my Israeli citizenship."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 86109.0,
      "end_time": 88276.0,
      "text": "But thanks to nationalism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 88300.0,
      "end_time": 92106.0,
      "text": "we can all care about one another and cooperate effectively."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 92450.0,
      "end_time": 93650.0,
      "text": "This is very good."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94930.0,
      "end_time": 99831.0,
      "text": "Some people, like John Lennon, imagine that without nationalism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 99855.0,
      "end_time": 103645.0,
      "text": "the world will be a peaceful paradise."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 104100.0,
      "end_time": 105438.0,
      "text": "But far more likely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 105462.0,
      "end_time": 110239.0,
      "text": "without nationalism, we would have been living in tribal chaos."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 110684.0,
      "end_time": 115819.0,
      "text": "If you look today at the most prosperous and peaceful countries in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 115843.0,
      "end_time": 120133.0,
      "text": "countries like Sweden and Switzerland and Japan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 120157.0,
      "end_time": 125119.0,
      "text": "you will see that they have a very strong sense of nationalism."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 125750.0,
      "end_time": 129910.0,
      "text": "In contrast, countries that lack a strong sense of nationalism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 129934.0,
      "end_time": 133355.0,
      "text": "like Congo and Somalia and Afghanistan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 133379.0,
      "end_time": 135553.0,
      "text": "tend to be violent and poor."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 136855.0,
      "end_time": 140993.0,
      "text": "So what is fascism, and how is it different from nationalism?"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 141941.0,
      "end_time": 147344.0,
      "text": "Well, nationalism tells me that my nation is unique,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 147368.0,
      "end_time": 151168.0,
      "text": "and that I have special obligations towards my nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 151641.0,
      "end_time": 157846.0,
      "text": "Fascism, in contrast, tells me that my nation is supreme,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 157871.0,
      "end_time": 161783.0,
      "text": "and that I have exclusive obligations towards it."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 162895.0,
      "end_time": 167726.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t need to care about anybody or anything other than my nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 168465.0,
      "end_time": 172680.0,
      "text": "Usually, of course, people have many identities"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 172920.0,
      "end_time": 174514.0,
      "text": "and loyalties to different groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 175360.0,
      "end_time": 179840.0,
      "text": "For example, I can be a good patriot, loyal to my country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 179864.0,
      "end_time": 183102.0,
      "text": "and at the same time, be loyal to my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 183126.0,
      "end_time": 185487.0,
      "text": "my neighborhood, my profession,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 185511.0,
      "end_time": 186971.0,
      "text": "humankind as a whole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 186995.0,
      "end_time": 188599.0,
      "text": "truth and beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 189370.0,
      "end_time": 193641.0,
      "text": "Of course, when I have different identities and loyalties,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 193665.0,
      "end_time": 196998.0,
      "text": "it sometimes creates conflicts and complications."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 197506.0,
      "end_time": 201140.0,
      "text": "But, well, who ever told you that life was easy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 201649.0,
      "end_time": 203689.0,
      "text": "Life is complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 203713.0,
      "end_time": 204863.0,
      "text": "Deal with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 206331.0,
      "end_time": 212331.0,
      "text": "Fascism is what happens when people try to ignore the complications"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 212355.0,
      "end_time": 215464.0,
      "text": "and to make life too easy for themselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 216128.0,
      "end_time": 221700.0,
      "text": "Fascism denies all identities except the national identity"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 221724.0,
      "end_time": 226833.0,
      "text": "and insists that I have obligations only towards my nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 227421.0,
      "end_time": 231525.0,
      "text": "If my nation demands that I sacrifice my family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 231549.0,
      "end_time": 233985.0,
      "text": "then I will sacrifice my family."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 234900.0,
      "end_time": 238283.0,
      "text": "If the nation demands that I kill millions of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 238307.0,
      "end_time": 240964.0,
      "text": "then I will kill millions of people."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 241442.0,
      "end_time": 247517.0,
      "text": "And if my nation demands that I betray truth and beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 247541.0,
      "end_time": 250564.0,
      "text": "then I should betray truth and beauty."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 251587.0,
      "end_time": 256113.0,
      "text": "For example, how does a fascist evaluate art?"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 256615.0,
      "end_time": 261904.0,
      "text": "How does a fascist decide whether a movie is a good movie or a bad movie?"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 262728.0,
      "end_time": 266900.0,
      "text": "Well, it&#39;s very, very, very simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 269188.0,
      "text": "There is really just one yardstick:"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 269593.0,
      "end_time": 273690.0,
      "text": "if the movie serves the interests of the nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 273930.0,
      "end_time": 274537.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a good movie;"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 274561.0,
      "end_time": 277744.0,
      "text": "if the movie doesn&#39;t serve the interests of the nation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 277768.0,
      "end_time": 278989.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a bad movie."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 279140.0,
      "end_time": 280164.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s it."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 280496.0,
      "end_time": 285383.0,
      "text": "Similarly, how does a fascist decide what to teach kids in school?"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 285877.0,
      "end_time": 287964.0,
      "text": "Again, it&#39;s very simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 287988.0,
      "end_time": 289933.0,
      "text": "There is just one yardstick:"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 289957.0,
      "end_time": 294902.0,
      "text": "you teach the kids whatever serves the interests of the nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 295323.0,
      "end_time": 297909.0,
      "text": "The truth doesn&#39;t matter at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 300372.0,
      "end_time": 305798.0,
      "text": "Now, the horrors of the Second World War and of the Holocaust remind us"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 305822.0,
      "end_time": 309955.0,
      "text": "of the terrible consequences of this way of thinking."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 310508.0,
      "end_time": 315530.0,
      "text": "But usually, when we talk about the ills of fascism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 315770.0,
      "end_time": 318370.0,
      "text": "we do so in an ineffective way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 318610.0,
      "end_time": 322799.0,
      "text": "because we tend to depict fascism as a hideous monster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 322823.0,
      "end_time": 326729.0,
      "text": "without really explaining what was so seductive about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 327284.0,
      "end_time": 331998.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a bit like these Hollywood movies that depict the bad guys --"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 332220.0,
      "end_time": 336450.0,
      "text": "Voldemort or Sauron or Darth Vader --"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 336690.0,
      "end_time": 338701.0,
      "text": "as ugly and mean and cruel."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 338725.0,
      "end_time": 341263.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re cruel even to their own supporters."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 341670.0,
      "end_time": 345291.0,
      "text": "When I see these movies, I never understand --"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 345315.0,
      "end_time": 351820.0,
      "text": "why would anybody be tempted to follow a disgusting creep like Voldemort?"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 352895.0,
      "end_time": 356411.0,
      "text": "The problem with evil is that in real life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 356435.0,
      "end_time": 359326.0,
      "text": "evil doesn&#39;t necessarily look ugly."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 359688.0,
      "end_time": 361580.0,
      "text": "It can look very beautiful."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 362354.0,
      "end_time": 365770.0,
      "text": "This is something that Christianity knew very well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 365101.0,
      "end_time": 368807.0,
      "text": "which is why in Christian art, as [opposed to] Hollywood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 368831.0,
      "end_time": 372699.0,
      "text": "Satan is usually depicted as a gorgeous hunk."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 373259.0,
      "end_time": 377855.0,
      "text": "This is why it&#39;s so difficult to resist the temptations of Satan,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 377879.0,
      "end_time": 382623.0,
      "text": "and why it is also difficult to resist the temptations of fascism."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 382980.0,
      "end_time": 385702.0,
      "text": "Fascism makes people see themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 385726.0,
      "end_time": 390969.0,
      "text": "as belonging to the most beautiful and most important thing in the world --"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 390993.0,
      "end_time": 392295.0,
      "text": "the nation."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 392319.0,
      "end_time": 393665.0,
      "text": "And then people think,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 393689.0,
      "end_time": 396878.0,
      "text": "\"Well, they taught us that fascism is ugly."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 397442.0,
      "end_time": 400466.0,
      "text": "But when I look in the mirror, I see something very beautiful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 400490.0,
      "end_time": 402681.0,
      "text": "so I can&#39;t be a fascist, right?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 403220.0,
      "end_time": 404173.0,
      "text": "Wrong."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 404197.0,
      "end_time": 405744.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the problem with fascism."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 405768.0,
      "end_time": 408387.0,
      "text": "When you look in the fascist mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 408411.0,
      "end_time": 412945.0,
      "text": "you see yourself as far more beautiful than you really are."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 413371.0,
      "end_time": 417664.0,
      "text": "In the 1930s, when Germans looked in the fascist mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 417688.0,
      "end_time": 421728.0,
      "text": "they saw Germany as the most beautiful thing in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 422244.0,
      "end_time": 425680.0,
      "text": "If today, Russians look in the fascist mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 425704.0,
      "end_time": 429263.0,
      "text": "they will see Russia as the most beautiful thing in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 429577.0,
      "end_time": 432705.0,
      "text": "And if Israelis look in the fascist mirror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 432729.0,
      "end_time": 437109.0,
      "text": "they will see Israel as the most beautiful thing in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 438657.0,
      "end_time": 443714.0,
      "text": "This does not mean that we are now facing a rerun of the 1930s."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 444304.0,
      "end_time": 447779.0,
      "text": "Fascism and dictatorships might come back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 447803.0,
      "end_time": 451420.0,
      "text": "but they will come back in a new form,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 451660.0,
      "end_time": 453806.0,
      "text": "a form which is much more relevant"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 453831.0,
      "end_time": 457640.0,
      "text": "to the new technological realities of the 21st century."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 458538.0,
      "end_time": 460850.0,
      "text": "In ancient times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 460109.0,
      "end_time": 464269.0,
      "text": "land was the most important asset in the world."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 464911.0,
      "end_time": 468775.0,
      "text": "Politics, therefore, was the struggle to control land."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 469141.0,
      "end_time": 475100.0,
      "text": "And dictatorship meant that all the land was owned by a single ruler"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 475250.0,
      "end_time": 476897.0,
      "text": "or by a small oligarch."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 477827.0,
      "end_time": 482646.0,
      "text": "And in the modern age, machines became more important than land."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 483347.0,
      "end_time": 486947.0,
      "text": "Politics became the struggle to control the machines."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 487354.0,
      "end_time": 489349.0,
      "text": "And dictatorship meant"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 489374.0,
      "end_time": 493284.0,
      "text": "that too many of the machines became concentrated"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 493308.0,
      "end_time": 496587.0,
      "text": "in the hands of the government or of a small elite."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 497109.0,
      "end_time": 501815.0,
      "text": "Now data is replacing both land and machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 501839.0,
      "end_time": 503950.0,
      "text": "as the most important asset."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 504600.0,
      "end_time": 509940.0,
      "text": "Politics becomes the struggle to control the flows of data."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 509964.0,
      "end_time": 512672.0,
      "text": "And dictatorship now means"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 512696.0,
      "end_time": 518476.0,
      "text": "that too much data is being concentrated in the hands of the government"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 518500.0,
      "end_time": 520419.0,
      "text": "or of a small elite."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 520871.0,
      "end_time": 525783.0,
      "text": "The greatest danger that now faces liberal democracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 525807.0,
      "end_time": 529770.0,
      "text": "is that the revolution in information technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 529101.0,
      "end_time": 533891.0,
      "text": "will make dictatorships more efficient than democracies."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 534760.0,
      "end_time": 536379.0,
      "text": "In the 20th century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 536403.0,
      "end_time": 541363.0,
      "text": "democracy and capitalism defeated fascism and communism"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 541387.0,
      "end_time": 546589.0,
      "text": "because democracy was better at processing data and making decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 547319.0,
      "end_time": 549685.0,
      "text": "Given 20th-century technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 549709.0,
      "end_time": 555743.0,
      "text": "it was simply inefficient to try and concentrate too much data"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 555768.0,
      "end_time": 558527.0,
      "text": "and too much power in one place."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 559244.0,
      "end_time": 563727.0,
      "text": "But it is not a law of nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 563751.0,
      "end_time": 569355.0,
      "text": "that centralized data processing is always less efficient"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 569379.0,
      "end_time": 571926.0,
      "text": "than distributed data processing."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 572605.0,
      "end_time": 576420.0,
      "text": "With the rise of artificial intelligence and machine learning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 576660.0,
      "end_time": 581903.0,
      "text": "it might become feasible to process enormous amounts of information"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 581927.0,
      "end_time": 584537.0,
      "text": "very efficiently in one place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 584561.0,
      "end_time": 587752.0,
      "text": "to take all the decisions in one place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 587776.0,
      "end_time": 592195.0,
      "text": "and then centralized data processing will be more efficient"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 592220.0,
      "end_time": 594420.0,
      "text": "than distributed data processing."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 595530.0,
      "end_time": 598813.0,
      "text": "And then the main handicap of authoritarian regimes"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 598837.0,
      "end_time": 600473.0,
      "text": "in the 20th century --"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 600498.0,
      "end_time": 605140.0,
      "text": "their attempt to concentrate all the information in one place --"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 605380.0,
      "end_time": 608404.0,
      "text": "it will become their greatest advantage."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 610768.0,
      "end_time": 615675.0,
      "text": "Another technological danger that threatens the future of democracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 615699.0,
      "end_time": 620858.0,
      "text": "is the merger of information technology with biotechnology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 620882.0,
      "end_time": 624887.0,
      "text": "which might result in the creation of algorithms"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 624911.0,
      "end_time": 629227.0,
      "text": "that know me better than I know myself."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 629688.0,
      "end_time": 631768.0,
      "text": "And once you have such algorithms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 631792.0,
      "end_time": 634641.0,
      "text": "an external system, like the government,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 634665.0,
      "end_time": 638189.0,
      "text": "cannot just predict my decisions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 638213.0,
      "end_time": 642134.0,
      "text": "it can also manipulate my feelings, my emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 642641.0,
      "end_time": 647886.0,
      "text": "A dictator may not be able to provide me with good health care,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 647910.0,
      "end_time": 651283.0,
      "text": "but he will be able to make me love him"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 651307.0,
      "end_time": 653974.0,
      "text": "and to make me hate the opposition."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 655370.0,
      "end_time": 660500.0,
      "text": "Democracy will find it difficult to survive such a development"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 660524.0,
      "end_time": 662674.0,
      "text": "because, in the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 662698.0,
      "end_time": 666824.0,
      "text": "democracy is not based on human rationality;"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 666849.0,
      "end_time": 669269.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s based on human feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 670355.0,
      "end_time": 672855.0,
      "text": "During elections and referendums,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 672879.0,
      "end_time": 675575.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re not being asked, \"What do you think?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 675998.0,
      "end_time": 679394.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re actually being asked, \"How do you feel?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 680228.0,
      "end_time": 684854.0,
      "text": "And if somebody can manipulate your emotions effectively,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 684879.0,
      "end_time": 688632.0,
      "text": "democracy will become an emotional puppet show."
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 690600.0,
      "end_time": 694521.0,
      "text": "So what can we do to prevent the return of fascism"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 694545.0,
      "end_time": 697194.0,
      "text": "and the rise of new dictatorships?"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 697990.0,
      "end_time": 704300.0,
      "text": "The number one question that we face is: Who controls the data?"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 704823.0,
      "end_time": 706497.0,
      "text": "If you are an engineer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 706522.0,
      "end_time": 710490.0,
      "text": "then find ways to prevent too much data"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 710514.0,
      "end_time": 713339.0,
      "text": "from being concentrated in too few hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 713752.0,
      "end_time": 716695.0,
      "text": "And find ways to make sure"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 716720.0,
      "end_time": 721133.0,
      "text": "the distributed data processing is at least as efficient"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 721157.0,
      "end_time": 723553.0,
      "text": "as centralized data processing."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 724770.0,
      "end_time": 727918.0,
      "text": "This will be the best safeguard for democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 727942.0,
      "end_time": 731268.0,
      "text": "As for the rest of us who are not engineers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 731292.0,
      "end_time": 734736.0,
      "text": "the number one question facing us"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 734760.0,
      "end_time": 739407.0,
      "text": "is how not to allow ourselves to be manipulated"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 739431.0,
      "end_time": 742237.0,
      "text": "by those who control the data."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 743387.0,
      "end_time": 747492.0,
      "text": "The enemies of liberal democracy, they have a method."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 747919.0,
      "end_time": 750290.0,
      "text": "They hack our feelings."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 750315.0,
      "end_time": 752767.0,
      "text": "Not our emails, not our bank accounts --"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 752791.0,
      "end_time": 757998.0,
      "text": "they hack our feelings of fear and hate and vanity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 758220.0,
      "end_time": 760450.0,
      "text": "and then use these feelings"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 760474.0,
      "end_time": 764426.0,
      "text": "to polarize and destroy democracy from within."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 764903.0,
      "end_time": 766823.0,
      "text": "This is actually a method"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 766847.0,
      "end_time": 771896.0,
      "text": "that Silicon Valley pioneered in order to sell us products."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 772381.0,
      "end_time": 777403.0,
      "text": "But now, the enemies of democracy are using this very method"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 777427.0,
      "end_time": 781151.0,
      "text": "to sell us fear and hate and vanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 781863.0,
      "end_time": 785522.0,
      "text": "They cannot create these feelings out of nothing."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 786212.0,
      "end_time": 790430.0,
      "text": "So they get to know our own preexisting weaknesses."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 790403.0,
      "end_time": 792974.0,
      "text": "And then use them against us."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 793482.0,
      "end_time": 796990.0,
      "text": "And it is therefore the responsibility of all of us"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 797140.0,
      "end_time": 799648.0,
      "text": "to get to know our weaknesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 799672.0,
      "end_time": 803307.0,
      "text": "and make sure that they do not become a weapon"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 803331.0,
      "end_time": 806214.0,
      "text": "in the hands of the enemies of democracy."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 807315.0,
      "end_time": 809863.0,
      "text": "Getting to know our own weaknesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 809887.0,
      "end_time": 815469.0,
      "text": "will also help us to avoid the trap of the fascist mirror."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 816204.0,
      "end_time": 820354.0,
      "text": "As we explained earlier, fascism exploits our vanity."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 820805.0,
      "end_time": 826550.0,
      "text": "It makes us see ourselves as far more beautiful than we really are."
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 826575.0,
      "end_time": 828420.0,
      "text": "This is the seduction."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 828424.0,
      "end_time": 830871.0,
      "text": "But if you really know yourself,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 830895.0,
      "end_time": 834363.0,
      "text": "you will not fall for this kind of flattery."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 834879.0,
      "end_time": 838942.0,
      "text": "If somebody puts a mirror in front of your eyes"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 838966.0,
      "end_time": 844260.0,
      "text": "that hides all your ugly bits and makes you see yourself"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 844500.0,
      "end_time": 848334.0,
      "text": "as far more beautiful and far more important"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 848358.0,
      "end_time": 849949.0,
      "text": "than you really are,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 849973.0,
      "end_time": 852837.0,
      "text": "just break that mirror."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 853696.0,
      "end_time": 854847.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 854871.0,
      "end_time": 861252.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 862677.0,
      "end_time": 864309.0,
      "text": "Chris Anderson: Yuval, thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 864333.0,
      "end_time": 865483.0,
      "text": "Goodness me."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 865958.0,
      "end_time": 867898.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s so nice to see you again."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 867922.0,
      "end_time": 869513.0,
      "text": "So, if I understand you right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 869537.0,
      "end_time": 872204.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re alerting us to two big dangers here."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 872228.0,
      "end_time": 876719.0,
      "text": "One is the possible resurgence of a seductive form of fascism,"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 876744.0,
      "end_time": 880998.0,
      "text": "but close to that, dictatorships that may not exactly be fascistic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 881220.0,
      "end_time": 883585.0,
      "text": "but control all the data."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 883609.0,
      "end_time": 885705.0,
      "text": "I wonder if there&#39;s a third concern"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 885729.0,
      "end_time": 887847.0,
      "text": "that some people here have already expressed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 887871.0,
      "end_time": 892768.0,
      "text": "which is where, not governments, but big corporations control all our data."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 892792.0,
      "end_time": 894101.0,
      "text": "What do you call that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 894125.0,
      "end_time": 896512.0,
      "text": "and how worried should we be about that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 896536.0,
      "end_time": 899875.0,
      "text": "Yuval Noah Harari: Well, in the end, there isn&#39;t such a big difference"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 899899.0,
      "end_time": 902325.0,
      "text": "between the corporations and the governments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 902349.0,
      "end_time": 905769.0,
      "text": "because, as I said, the questions is: Who controls the data?"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 905793.0,
      "end_time": 907188.0,
      "text": "This is the real government."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 907212.0,
      "end_time": 909656.0,
      "text": "If you call it a corporation or a government --"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 909680.0,
      "end_time": 912834.0,
      "text": "if it&#39;s a corporation and it really controls the data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 912859.0,
      "end_time": 914787.0,
      "text": "this is our real government."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 914811.0,
      "end_time": 917878.0,
      "text": "So the difference is more apparent than real."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 918529.0,
      "end_time": 921387.0,
      "text": "CA: But somehow, at least with corporations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 921411.0,
      "end_time": 924930.0,
      "text": "you can imagine market mechanisms where they can be taken down."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 924954.0,
      "end_time": 926871.0,
      "text": "I mean, if consumers just decide"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 926895.0,
      "end_time": 929649.0,
      "text": "that the company is no longer operating in their interest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 929673.0,
      "end_time": 931586.0,
      "text": "it does open the door to another market."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 931610.0,
      "end_time": 933156.0,
      "text": "It seems easier to imagine that"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 933180.0,
      "end_time": 936330.0,
      "text": "than, say, citizens rising up and taking down a government"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 936355.0,
      "end_time": 937967.0,
      "text": "that is in control of everything."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 937991.0,
      "end_time": 939545.0,
      "text": "YNH: Well, we are not there yet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 939570.0,
      "end_time": 944728.0,
      "text": "but again, if a corporation really knows you better than you know yourself --"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 944752.0,
      "end_time": 950600.0,
      "text": "at least that it can manipulate your own deepest emotions and desires,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 950300.0,
      "end_time": 951696.0,
      "text": "and you won&#39;t even realize --"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 951720.0,
      "end_time": 954299.0,
      "text": "you will think this is your authentic self."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 954768.0,
      "end_time": 958823.0,
      "text": "So in theory, yes, in theory, you can rise against a corporation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 958847.0,
      "end_time": 962579.0,
      "text": "just as, in theory, you can rise against a dictatorship."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 962982.0,
      "end_time": 966265.0,
      "text": "But in practice, it is extremely difficult."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 967281.0,
      "end_time": 971363.0,
      "text": "CA: So in \"Homo Deus,\" you argue that this would be the century"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 971387.0,
      "end_time": 974797.0,
      "text": "when humans kind of became gods,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 974822.0,
      "end_time": 977815.0,
      "text": "either through development of artificial intelligence"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 977839.0,
      "end_time": 980768.0,
      "text": "or through genetic engineering."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 980792.0,
      "end_time": 986260.0,
      "text": "Has this prospect of political system shift, collapse"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 986284.0,
      "end_time": 988948.0,
      "text": "impacted your view on that possibility?"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 989553.0,
      "end_time": 992648.0,
      "text": "YNH: Well, I think it makes it even more likely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 992672.0,
      "end_time": 995601.0,
      "text": "and more likely that it will happen faster,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 995625.0,
      "end_time": 1000648.0,
      "text": "because in times of crisis, people are willing to take risks"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 1000670.0,
      "end_time": 1002654.0,
      "text": "that they wouldn&#39;t otherwise take."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 1002680.0,
      "end_time": 1005497.0,
      "text": "And people are willing to try"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 1005520.0,
      "end_time": 1009393.0,
      "text": "all kinds of high-risk, high-gain technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 1009760.0,
      "end_time": 1013990.0,
      "text": "So these kinds of crises might serve the same function"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 1014140.0,
      "end_time": 1017228.0,
      "text": "as the two world wars in the 20th century."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 1017250.0,
      "end_time": 1020462.0,
      "text": "The two world wars greatly accelerated"
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 1020490.0,
      "end_time": 1024102.0,
      "text": "the development of new and dangerous technologies."
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 1024119.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1027403.9999999999,
      "text": "And the same thing might happen in the 21st century."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 1027720.0,
      "end_time": 1031616.0,
      "text": "I mean, you need to be a little crazy to run too fast,"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 1031640.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1033965.0000000001,
      "text": "let&#39;s say, with genetic engineering."
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 1033990.0,
      "end_time": 1037099.0,
      "text": "But now you have more and more crazy people"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 1037119.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1039800.9999999999,
      "text": "in charge of different countries in the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 1039829.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1042896.9999999999,
      "text": "so the chances are getting higher, not lower."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 1043650.0000000001,
      "end_time": 1047124.0000000001,
      "text": "CA: So, putting it all together, Yuval, you&#39;ve got this unique vision."
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 1047359.9999999999,
      "end_time": 1048623.0,
      "text": "Roll the clock forward 30 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 1048650.0,
      "end_time": 1051912.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s your guess -- does humanity just somehow scrape through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 1051930.0,
      "end_time": 1055686.0,
      "text": "look back and say, \"Wow, that was a close thing. We did it!\""
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 1055930.0,
      "end_time": 1056529.0,
      "text": "Or not?"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 1056550.0,
      "end_time": 1060398.0,
      "text": "YNH: So far, we&#39;ve managed to overcome all the previous crises."
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 1060430.0,
      "end_time": 1063249.0,
      "text": "And especially if you look at liberal democracy"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 1063270.0,
      "end_time": 1066214.0,
      "text": "and you think things are bad now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 1066240.0,
      "end_time": 1072706.0,
      "text": "just remember how much worse things looked in 1938 or in 1968."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 1072730.0,
      "end_time": 1075721.0,
      "text": "So this is really nothing, this is just a small crisis."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 1076170.0,
      "end_time": 1078139.0,
      "text": "But you can never know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 1078160.0,
      "end_time": 1080291.0,
      "text": "because, as a historian,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 1080310.0,
      "end_time": 1085885.0,
      "text": "I know that you should never underestimate human stupidity."
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 1085110.0,
      "end_time": 1086265.0,
      "text": "(Laughter) (Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 1086290.0,
      "end_time": 1090293.0,
      "text": "It is one of the most powerful forces that shape history."
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 1091430.0,
      "end_time": 1094295.0,
      "text": "CA: Yuval, it&#39;s been an absolute delight to have you with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 1094320.0,
      "end_time": 1096137.0,
      "text": "Thank you for making the virtual trip."
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 1096160.0,
      "end_time": 1098357.0,
      "text": "Have a great evening there in Tel Aviv."
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 1098600.0,
      "end_time": 1099211.0,
      "text": "Yuval Harari!"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 1099230.0,
      "end_time": 1100605.0,
      "text": "YNH: Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 1100640.0,
      "end_time": 1101790.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}